---
const benefits = [
  { text: "Online Creative Classes" },
  { text: "Skill Expansion" },
  { text: "Hands-On Learning" },
  { text: "Flexible Learning" },
  { text: "Personalized Experience" },
  { text: "Discover New Talents" },
  { text: "Curated Curriculum" },
  { text: "Interactive Assignments" },
  { text: "Creative Community" },
];
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="px-8 py-12 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-32 max-w-7xl lg:py-12 items-center lg:flex">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-xl lg:flex-shrink-0 lg:pt-8">
      <p class="text-4xl font-semibold font-display text-blue-950">
        Exploring the reasons to choose Enlightr for your learning journey
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4 max-w-sm text-base">
        Are you in search of an avenue to broaden your skill set and delve into
        the realms of your creative potential? Look no further.
      </p>
      <ul
        class="list-none text-slate-500 space-y-2 mt-10 text-sm grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        {
          benefits.map((benefit) => (
            <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500">‚è§</span> {benefit.text}
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-10 max-w-sm text-base">
        Our immersive creative courses offer you a hands-on experience that not
        only facilitates learning at a pace that suits you but also unveils the
        treasures of untapped talents waiting to be discovered.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-16 flex max-w-2xl sm:mt-24 lg:ml-10 lg:mr-0 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none">
      <div class="max-w-3xl flex-none sm:max-w-5xl lg:max-w-none">
        <img
          src="/dashboard.svg"
          alt="#"
          width="2432"
          height="1442"
          class="w-[76rem] rounded-3xl bg-slate-100 overflow-hidden"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
